<TEXT>
<P>
PARIS, August 12 (Xinhua) -- The International Amateur Athletic
Federation (IAAF) said on Thursday it would investigate Bernard
Barmasai following his claim that a fellow Kenyan had allowed him
to win the 3,000 meters steeplechase at Wednesday's Zurich grand
prix.
</P>
