a dispute over Israel's delay in applying the Wye Plantation
agreements, Israeli air raids in Lebanon, and the status of
Jerusalem.
</P>
<P>
France has expressed its hope that Israeli Prime Minister Ehud
Barak can re-launch the peace process, which has been paralyzed
for four years under former Prime Minister Benjamin Netanyahu.
