National Australia Bank which jumped 29.8 cents to 23.088
Australian dollars while the Commonwealth Bank continued to fall,
closing down 17.5 cents to 23.335 Australian dollars. The ANZ
dropped 0.2 of a cent to 10.178 Australian dollars and Westpac was
steady at 9.86 Australian dollars.
</P>
