million U.S. dollars) to complete 35 technical renovation projects.
</P>
<P>
Thus far, Tibet has six listed companies which have raised a
total of 970 million yuan (about 117 million U.S. dollars) through
issuing shares.
</P>
<P>
In Shannan Prefecture whose State-owned foreign trade
corporations and enterprises, which used to suffer great losses,
achieved 17 million yuan (about 2 million U.S. dollars) in profits
after adopting a series of reform measures.  
