<TEXT>
<P>
ISLAMABAD, August 13 (Xinhua) -- At least 10 people are feared
to have been killed and many more injured in fierce storm and
torrential rains which hit Kasur in eastern part of Punjab
province late Thursday night.
</P>
<P>
