<HEADLINE> Brazil Expects Huge Investments From Overseas </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
RIO DE JANEIRO, August 12 (Xinhua) -- Brazil hopes to receive
165 billion U.S. dollars from foreign investors for infrastructure
projects between 2000 and 2007, a study showed.
</P>
<P>
